description:
This Course is about how to make successful debut on freelancer.com . This course teach you how to make a attractive bid on freelancer.com.

All videos are screencast video.This course is short course of 30 minute duration. Course is divided in two parts . First is introduction about author and how to create email id before signing up on freelancer.

Second part is all about how to bid and success secretes .

This course will help you enhancing your rating on freelancer.com.
title: How to become successful freelancer on Freelancer
